Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.20,0:01:03.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是个适合埋头苦读的黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.20,0:01:03.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was a dark and studious night
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.83,0:01:08.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你帮我突击明天的驾考
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:08.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for helping me cram for my driver's exam
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.75,0:01:13.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第307题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:13.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Question 307:
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.26,0:01:17.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二十点转向要打哪个档位
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.26,0:01:15.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What gear should you use
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:17.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when making a twenty-point turn?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.55,0:01:19.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.55,0:01:19.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.60,0:01:22.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二十点除以档位x
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.60,0:01:22.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Twenty points divided by X number of gears
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.77,0:01:25.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,乘以半钢子午线轮胎半径
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.77,0:01:25.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,times the radius of a steel belted tire
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.46,0:01:48.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,被纸划到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.46,0:01:48.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Paper cut
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.42,0:01:56.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.42,0:01:56.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pretty
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.68,0:01:59.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黑夜中有一傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.68,0:01:59.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If a fool in the dark of night
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.93,0:02:02.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,借着惨白的月光涂鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:02.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,should doodle by the moon's pale light
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.93,0:02:06.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就会化为铅笔狼人  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.93,0:02:06.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a WereDoodle they shall become, alright?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.85,0:02:10.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,第二天早上
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.53,0:02:17.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,昨晚肯定是学得太拼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.53,0:02:17.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That must've been one wild night of studying
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.36,0:02:18.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我什么东西都不记得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.36,0:02:18.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't remember a thing
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.87,0:02:22.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你今早好吗  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.87,0:02:22.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How are you this morning, Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.95,0:02:28.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的驾考
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.95,0:02:28.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My boating exam
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.50,0:02:29.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:29.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm late
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:33.25,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(906,448)}滑浪学校
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.25,0:02:35.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望大家都有好好学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:35.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope everyone studied
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.71,0:02:38.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝没来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.71,0:02:38.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob's not here?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.80,0:02:40.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多半他弃考了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:40.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe he quit
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.43,0:02:41.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多半我自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.43,0:02:41.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm free
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.14,0:02:42.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多半
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:42.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.01,0:02:44.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉迟到了  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.01,0:02:44.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.77,0:02:49.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,远不如我心中的遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:49.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not as sorry as I am
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.23,0:02:53.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,同学们  考试开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:53.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, class, you may start the exam
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:59.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,答了很多试题之后
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.92,0:03:12.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好个怪疹子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.92,0:03:12.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a weird rash
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.38,0:03:14.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:14.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.79,0:03:16.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得去上卫生间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:16.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need to go to the restroom
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.42,0:03:17.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可现在还在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:17.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But we're in the middle of a
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.76,0:03:19.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,考试
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.76,0:03:19.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,test
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.22,0:03:23.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:23.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:46.58,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(392,338)}请洗鳍
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.04,0:03:57.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这玩意谁画的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:57.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who drew this?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.42,0:03:59.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不长那样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:03:59.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't look like that
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.16,0:04:27.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,同学们停笔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:27.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pencils down, class
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.66,0:04:31.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,第二天早上
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.62,0:04:34.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:34.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.17,0:04:36.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:36.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.04,0:04:38.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,图书馆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.04,0:04:38.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The library
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.46,0:04:39.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,图书馆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:39.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The library?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.34,0:04:42.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我应该是逾期了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:42.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I'm overdue
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.34,0:04:43.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:43.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to leave
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:45.55,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(700,298)}裤头村图书馆
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.30,0:04:48.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好穿好衣服去上班
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:48.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I better get dressed and get to work
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.47,0:04:50.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,启动应急裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.47,0:04:50.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Activate emergency pants
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.93,0:04:53.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:53.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.89,0:04:55.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能载我一程去上班吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:55.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you give me a lift to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:02.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,很多小时后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:05.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(780,446)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.36,0:05:05.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天太疯狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:05.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a crazy day
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.70,0:05:07.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能回来做蟹黄堡真好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:07.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's good to get back to flipping patties
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.95,0:05:10.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  能帮我顶下班吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:10.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob, can you cover for me?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.83,0:05:13.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得休息一下  来恢复理智
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:13.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's time for my sanity break
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.87,0:05:17.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一次打两份工吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:17.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two jobs at once?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.13,0:05:20.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美梦成真了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:20.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A dream come true
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.17,0:05:21.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随你的便
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:21.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Knock yourself out
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:21.55,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(960,920)}砸 晕 你 自 己
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.63,0:05:23.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:23.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, really
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.22,0:05:24.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,砸下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.22,0:05:24.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想要来点一些吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like to order some food
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.68,0:05:29.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我肚子出现紧急情况了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:29.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a belly emergency
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.81,0:05:32.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:32.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.07,0:05:45.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好厉害的魔术
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:45.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice magic trick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.74,0:05:46.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:46.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do it again
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.90,0:05:49.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  乐谱忘带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:49.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I forgot my sheet music
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.49,0:05:51.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个三心二意的白痴哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:51.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where is that scatterbrained sap?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.49,0:05:53.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:53.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.54,0:05:55.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就在这呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:55.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm right here
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.12,0:05:57.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:57.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.04,0:06:03.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个小白痴往我点餐本上乱涂乱画
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:03.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That little twerp doodled all over my order pad
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.84,0:06:09.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,难道是那个铅笔人回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:09.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that DoodleBob thing back?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.31,0:06:16.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  更严重了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:16.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, it's even worse
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.95,0:06:37.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免费蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:37.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Free Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.46,0:06:42.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有点潦草了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:42.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A little sketchy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.51,0:06:49.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:49.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in the name of outboard motors is going on here?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.93,0:06:54.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我珍贵的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:54.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me precious money
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.81,0:07:02.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你把我的小宝贝们怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:02.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did you do to me little darlings?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.99,0:07:09.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的壳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:09.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me carapace
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:34.68,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(610,802)}露齿牙膏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:43.90,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(344,216)}公交站
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.73,0:07:50.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放倒我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:50.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am upended
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.74,0:07:56.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那只可怕的生物是什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:56.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What was that horrible creature?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.78,0:07:58.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我以前见过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:07:58.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've seen this before
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.66,0:08:01.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当时我还在海军服役
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:08:01.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in me old navy days
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.71,0:08:04.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海军生涯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:04.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Old navy days?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.21,0:08:06.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你上哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:06.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where have you been?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.59,0:08:10.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他很明显跟我们其他人一样被袭击了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:10.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He was obviously attacked, like the rest of us
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.76,0:08:15.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,罪魁祸首正是  邪恶的铅笔狼人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:15.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,by a vicious WereDoodle
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.05,0:08:18.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泰迪犬人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.05,0:08:18.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A bear poodle?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.10,0:08:18.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:18.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.22,0:08:21.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是铅笔狼人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:21.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A WereDoodle
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.56,0:08:26.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有一样东西能阻止铅笔狼人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:26.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There be only one thing that can stop a WereDoodle
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:33.70,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1268,160)}若遇见铅笔狼人请使用
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.48,0:08:30.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,银色橡皮擦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:30.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A silver eraser
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.07,0:08:32.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁想加入我的武装队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:32.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who wants to join me posse
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.11,0:08:35.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,永远擦掉这只铅笔狼人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:35.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and erase this WereDoodle for good?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.03,0:08:40.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起逮着那个二维讨厌鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:40.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get that two-dimensional twerp
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.08,0:08:43.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,算我一个  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:43.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Count me in, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.79,0:08:45.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好几周没加入武装队了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:45.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I haven't been in a posse in weeks
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.83,0:08:47.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很高兴你能入队  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:47.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Glad to have you aboard, boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.04,0:08:50.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但也得先穿好衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:50.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But put some clothes on
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.46,0:08:52.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就穿  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:52.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will do, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.17,0:08:55.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,启动备用应急裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:55.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Activating backup emergency pants
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.64,0:09:04.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,石墨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:04.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Graphite
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.27,0:09:07.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:07.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's close
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.44,0:09:08.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铅笔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:08.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pencils
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.61,0:09:11.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来买现削的铅笔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:11.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get your freshly sharpened pencils
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.96,0:09:30.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:30.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.89,0:09:43.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要画漫画吗  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:43.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Care for a caricature, sir?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.48,0:09:56.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要说声不用就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:56.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All you had to say was no thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.66,0:10:02.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吊挂到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:02.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am suspended
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.58,0:10:10.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铅笔狼人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:10.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,WereDoodle
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.08,0:10:12.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这边有银色橡皮擦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:12.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got a silver eraser here
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.29,0:10:15.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且我还敢使出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:15.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'm not afraid to use it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.81,0:10:30.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铅笔人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:30.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,DoodleBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.77,0:10:35.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它应该是想告诉我们什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:35.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think it's trying to tell us something
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.78,0:10:40.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他说铅笔狼人很害怕  还被误解了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:39.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He said the WereDoodle is frightened
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:40.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and misunderstood
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.49,0:10:42.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:42.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.74,0:10:44.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是铅笔人的老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:44.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm DoodleBob's wife
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.16,0:10:46.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,告诉他们吧  老公
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:46.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell them, dear
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.25,0:10:52.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他很抱歉铅笔狼人造成了这么多麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:52.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's sorry WereDoodle caused so much trouble
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.67,0:10:53.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说对吧  老公
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:53.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, dear?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.21,0:10:55.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他会解除诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:55.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He'll remove the curse
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.63,0:10:58.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把人家变回正常人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:58.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and turn it back into a normal person
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.64,0:11:07.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是说好要把他变回正常人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:07.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Didn't she say a normal person?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.52,0:11:08.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:08.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.60,0:11:10.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就是那个铅笔狼人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:10.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You were the WereDoodle?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.35,0:11:11.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:11.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.02,0:11:13.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太丢脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:13.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How embarrassing
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.56,0:11:17.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铅笔狼人的威胁解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:17.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The menace of the WereDoodle is over
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.36,0:11:19.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为铅笔人欢呼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:19.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Huzzah for DoodleBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.99,0:11:21.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:21.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Huzzah
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.03,0:11:24.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多谢你帮忙  铅笔人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:24.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the help, DoodleBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.74,0:11:27.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,被纸划到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:27.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Paper cut
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.62,0:11:30.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来铅笔天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:30.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on down to Pencil Paradise
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.12,0:11:32.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,满足你所有铅笔购买需求
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:32.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for all your pencil needs
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:49.56,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H00FFC1&}猩猩皮套节
