Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:10.33,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1538,188)}日历
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.71,0:12:19.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:19.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.88,0:12:20.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:20.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.39,0:12:28.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,猩猩皮套节
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:28.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gorilla Suit Day
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.10,0:12:30.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有帽子没
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:30.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got the hat?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.27,0:12:36.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有皮套没  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:36.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got the suit, baby?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.75,0:12:54.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:54.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.00,0:12:57.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帮我拉拉链
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:57.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Zip me up?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.09,0:13:04.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有根银色的小薯条
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:04.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A little silver french fry
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.51,0:13:05.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,留着等会儿当点心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:05.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A snack for later
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.01,0:13:10.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我皮套怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:10.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's my costume?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.27,0:13:16.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差点就把我给骗到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:16.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You almost fooled me there
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.73,0:13:23.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来骗大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:23.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's fool everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.45,0:13:26.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回来  大猩猩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:26.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come back, gorilla
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.79,0:13:36.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:36.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh no
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.25,0:13:38.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的  大猩猩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:38.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My "gorilla"
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.13,0:13:40.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,逃出动物园了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:40.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,has escaped from the zoo
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.21,0:13:42.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快回来  大猩猩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.21,0:13:42.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come back here, "gorilla"
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.46,0:13:45.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大猩猩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.46,0:13:45.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gorilla?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.18,0:13:49.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大猩猩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:49.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gorilla
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.14,0:13:51.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大猩猩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:51.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gorilla
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.35,0:13:56.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有发狂的大猩猩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:56.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mad gorilla
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.11,0:14:07.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要靠近它嘴巴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:07.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't get near his mouth
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.24,0:14:10.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这头大猩猩可饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:10.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's a hungry gorilla
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:18.29,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(894,158)}便宜货超市
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.29,0:14:20.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们把大家都骗到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:20.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We fooled everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.04,0:14:22.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:22.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We sure did
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.34,0:14:24.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来该玩的都玩完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:24.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess the fun is over
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.96,0:14:27.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正我现在也该去上班了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:27.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's time for me to go to work anyway
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.67,0:14:28.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帮我解开拉链
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.67,0:14:28.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Unzip me?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.06,0:14:35.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拉链被某个白痴给弄坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:35.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Some idiot broke the zipper
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.06,0:14:38.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得把它给锯开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:38.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll have to saw it off
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.65,0:14:41.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没那时间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:41.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No time
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.98,0:14:43.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只能装成大猩猩过去上班了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:43.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just go to work as a gorilla
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.86,0:14:44.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:44.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See ya
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:51.45,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(516,364)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.45,0:14:53.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:53.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.08,0:14:54.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并不安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:54.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, it isn't
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.91,0:14:57.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,戴着头套不方便看东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.91,0:14:57.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure is hard to see with this mask on
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.21,0:14:59.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正不管穿不穿皮套
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:14:59.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But suit or no suit
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.71,0:15:01.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在都得来做蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:01.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's time to make the patties
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.54,0:15:03.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铲铲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:03.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spatty?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.00,0:15:05.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铲铲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:05.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spatty
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.71,0:15:08.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.71,0:15:08.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you are
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.13,0:15:09.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:09.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.26,0:15:11.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我需要肉饼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:11.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll need patties
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.51,0:15:14.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蔬菜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:14.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,veggies
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.14,0:15:18.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,面包
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:18.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,buns
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.14,0:15:20.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一点点这个  一点点那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:20.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Little bit of this, little bit of that
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.23,0:15:20.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:20.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.89,0:15:21.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,瞧好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:21.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,voilà
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.44,0:15:23.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看着挺对劲的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:23.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That looks right
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.99,0:15:28.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:28.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Was it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.95,0:15:31.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:31.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Order up
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.00,0:15:41.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:41.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, why are you
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.17,0:15:46.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是头大猩猩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:46.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a gorilla?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.63,0:15:50.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是头大腥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:50.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A "goriller"?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.47,0:15:56.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不是大腥  我是大餐厅的厨子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.47,0:15:56.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not a "goriller," I'm a griller
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.85,0:15:58.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我海绵宝宝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:58.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's me, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.60,0:16:00.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是脱不掉这身猩猩皮套而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:00.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just can't get this gorilla suit off
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.52,0:16:01.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:01.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.73,0:16:03.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,果不其然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:03.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Typical
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.90,0:16:06.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,野生动物禁止入内  假的也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:06.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No wild animals allowed, even fake ones
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.02,0:16:07.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我回家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:07.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now go home
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.98,0:16:12.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脱掉这身猴子皮套才可以回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:12.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and don't come back until you take that monkey suit off
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.03,0:16:14.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  其实大猩猩不算猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:14.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually, Mr. K, gorillas aren't monkeys
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.32,0:16:15.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它们属于
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:15.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,they're classified as--
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.12,0:16:16.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:16.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get out
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.87,0:16:24.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一时半会脱不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:24.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, until I get the suit off
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.67,0:16:26.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不如来好好玩一把
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:26.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I might as well enjoy it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:30.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1508,262)}公交
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.27,0:16:42.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,165,,我们正在现场直播报道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:42.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,110,,We are live on the scene
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:17:00.79,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(228,278)}直播
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:55.99,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\an3\pos(1812,840)}发狂大猩猩\N于裤头村袭击婴儿
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.81,0:16:46.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,165,,一只撒野的大猩猩正在袭击一名婴儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:46.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,110,,where a rampaging wild gorilla is attacking a baby
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.40,0:16:47.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,165,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:47.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,110,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.40,0:16:48.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,165,,请问一下  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:48.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,110,,Excuse me, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.40,0:16:49.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,165,,你是饲养员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:49.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,110,,Are you a zookeeper?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.32,0:16:52.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,165,,没错  我就是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:52.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,110,,Why, yes, I am
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.28,0:16:56.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,165,,我的大猩猩逃出动物园了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:56.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,110,,My gorilla has escaped from the zoo
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.99,0:17:00.74,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\an3\pos(1812,840)}饲养员确认\N大猩猩是邪恶的
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.20,0:16:57.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,165,,情况就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:57.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,110,,There you have it, folks
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.49,0:17:00.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,165,,每位家长最可怕的噩梦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:17:00.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,110,,Every parent's worst nightmare
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.16,0:17:03.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接下来的任务交给动物管理局
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:03.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Animal control will take over from here
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.29,0:17:06.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:06.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.17,0:17:07.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想办法救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.17,0:17:07.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do something
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.50,0:17:09.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.50,0:17:09.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.42,0:17:11.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不会破坏恶作剧的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:11.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I won't ruin the prank
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.92,0:17:14.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:14.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:22.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1374,332)}裤头村动物园
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.26,0:17:19.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都说过我真的不是大猩猩了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:19.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told you, I'm not a real gorilla
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.85,0:17:22.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天可是猩猩皮套节
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:22.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Today is Gorilla Suit Day
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.02,0:17:24.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大猩猩都用这套话术
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:24.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's what all the gorillas say
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.48,0:17:26.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回里面待着去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:26.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now get back in there
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.56,0:17:31.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别给我犟了  你个顽固的灵长类
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:31.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Settle down, you pigheaded primate
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.24,0:17:42.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  猩猩们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.24,0:17:42.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, gorillas
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.79,0:17:44.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.79,0:17:44.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.88,0:17:50.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宝贝快看  有大猩猩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.88,0:17:50.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, hon, gorillas
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.75,0:17:53.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完全没准备  不过我尽力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:53.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't prepare anything but I'll do my best
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.19,0:18:09.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有免费花生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:09.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Free peanuts?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.94,0:18:12.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不脱这身皮套了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:12.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm never taking this suit off
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.54,0:18:32.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们到了  菲菲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:32.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here we are, Fifi
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.54,0:18:34.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该吃好吃的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:34.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time for yum-yums
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.80,0:18:38.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还能炫耀新买的这身金黄毛衣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:38.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you can show off your new gold sweater
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:40.68,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(854,166)}菜单
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.97,0:18:43.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,菲菲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:43.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fifi
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.14,0:18:49.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冒犯到我虫子了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.14,0:18:49.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My worm is offended
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.19,0:18:50.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:50.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.27,0:18:53.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都叫你脱掉这身猩猩皮套了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:53.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I said take that gorilla suit off
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.79,0:19:07.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你个畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.79,0:19:07.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, you animal
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.33,0:19:09.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那些蟹黄堡的钱得从你工资扣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.33,0:19:09.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those patties are coming out of your pay
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.13,0:19:14.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可炸不了我  我都没被暴打
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:14.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't fry me, I'm not even battered
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:14.63,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1292,920)}裹 面 糊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.13,0:19:23.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝今天的表现比平常还诡异
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:23.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob sure is acting weirder than usual today
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.02,0:19:29.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:29.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.31,0:19:30.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放我下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:30.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put me down
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.64,0:19:33.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可骗不到人  光凭你这
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:33.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not fooling anyone with your
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.90,0:19:44.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我恨猩猩皮套节
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:44.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hate Gorilla Suit Day
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.96,0:19:59.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,长官  发现大猩猩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:19:59.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Chief, we found the gorilla
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.55,0:20:00.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请求进一步指示
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:00.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Requesting orders
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.26,0:20:06.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求救
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:06.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mayday
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.52,0:20:15.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们正在泡芙老师的灯塔现场报道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.52,0:20:15.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We are live at Mrs. Puff's lighthouse
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.94,0:20:19.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又一头出逃的大猩猩正在此大搞破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:19.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where another escaped gorilla is wreaking havoc
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.74,0:20:21.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我身边的还是这位大猩猩饲养员
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.74,0:20:21.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With me again is the gorilla's zookeeper
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.37,0:20:27.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:27.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.87,0:20:33.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们这个恶作剧好像做得有点过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:33.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think we might be taking this prank a little too far
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.42,0:20:35.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我本来还要吃这个的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:35.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was gonna eat this
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.04,0:20:37.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过貌似可以拿它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,0:20:37.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but perhaps it could be used
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.92,0:20:41.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当拉链来用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.92,0:20:41.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as some sort of zipping implement
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.88,0:20:43.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就来帮你把这身皮套脱下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:43.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So let's try and get that suit off ya
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.22,0:20:46.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:46.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here we go
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.85,0:20:50.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:50.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.35,0:20:53.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你什么时候开始穿的平角裤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:53.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Since when do you wear boxers?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.15,0:21:02.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,十二点钟方向掉了只大猩猩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:02.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Falling gorilla at 12 o'clock
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.08,0:21:16.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脆脆的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:16.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Crunchy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.09,0:21:21.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.09,0:21:21.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.17,0:21:22.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要来一起吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.17,0:21:22.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Care to join us?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.18,0:21:29.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我今天虱子吃得够多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.18,0:21:29.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I've eaten enough lice today
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.68,0:21:30.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.68,0:21:30.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.77,0:21:36.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这身皮套脱不掉  还怎么回去上班
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:36.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How can I go back to work if I can't get this suit off?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.65,0:21:42.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.65,0:21:42.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got an idea
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:55.62,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(410,728)}裤头村皮套供应\N黄色海绵人\N小号
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.20,0:21:54.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一件黄色海绵人皮套
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:54.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One Yellow Sponge Person costume
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.83,0:21:55.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.83,0:21:55.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perfect
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.87,0:21:58.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.87,0:21:58.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.58,0:21:59.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,焕然一新
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.58,0:21:59.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good as new
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.92,0:22:02.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.92,0:22:02.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, you're back
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.17,0:22:03.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.17,0:22:03.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yup
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.71,0:22:05.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且还正是时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.71,0:22:05.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And just in time, too
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.38,0:22:09.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为你也知道  明天可是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.38,0:22:09.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because as you know, tomorrow is
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.09,0:22:12.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,袋鼠皮套节
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.09,0:22:12.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kangaroo Suit Day
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.10,0:22:13.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都迫不及待了  不想等到明早
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:13.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't wait until morning
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.97,0:22:16.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来抢先跳一跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.97,0:22:16.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get a jump on it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.70,0:22:34.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这辈子都再也不想看到一头大猩猩了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.70,0:22:34.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I never see another gorilla, it'll be too soon
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.79,0:22:39.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.79,0:22:39.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh no
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.08,0:22:41.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有一头
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.08,0:22:41.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another one
